title.rendered: FanDuel Kentucky Promo Code: Get $100 Off on NFL Sunday Ticket

content.rendered:

Kentucky Pre-Launch: Get $100 in Bonus Bets + $100 Off NFL Sunday Ticket!

Claim Offer
Disclaimer

Fanduel Kentucky promo code – get your $100 welcome bonus

FanDuel Kentucky will offer many perks for new bettors who claim a FanDuel promo code. The sportsbook boasts a vast range of betting markets and responsible gaming resources. FanDuel also offers competitive odds and is one of the most user-friendly apps in the industry.

To claim the FanDuel Kentucky prelaunch bonus, all you need to do is fill out a brief registration form and confirm your eligibility. You will immediately qualify for $100 in bonus bets + $100 off NFL Sunday Ticket. Bonuses can be redeemed when sports betting goes live on September 28.

The winnings from the first-time deposit bonus can be withdrawn as soon as the bonus bet is settled. This is a very quick turnaround time, and it is one of the best features of this bonus offer.
